---
// モダンテーマのプロフィールページ
---

<main class="modern-profile">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="page-title">プロフィール</h1>

    <section class="profile-intro">
      <div class="intro-content">
        <h2 class="intro-title">山田太郎</h2>
        <p class="intro-subtitle">地域のために全力で働きます</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="profile-section">
      <h2 class="section-heading">基本情報</h2>
      <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="info-item">
          <div class="info-label">氏名</div>
          <div class="info-value">山田 太郎（やまだ たろう）</div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <div class="info-label">生年月日</div>
          <div class="info-value">1975年4月15日</div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <div class="info-label">出身地</div>
          <div class="info-value">東京都</div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <div class="info-label">学歴</div>
          <div class="info-value">○○大学法学部卒業</div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <div class="info-label">趣味</div>
          <div class="info-value">読書、ジョギング</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="profile-section">
      <h2 class="section-heading">経歴</h2>
      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">1998年</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">○○大学法学部卒業</div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">1998年</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">民間企業入社</div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">2005年</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">地域NPO法人設立に参画</div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">2010年</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">市議会議員初当選</div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">2014年</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">市議会議員再選（2期目）</div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">2018年</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">市議会議員再選（3期目）</div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">2022年</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">市議会議員再選（4期目、現在に至る）</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="profile-section">
      <h2 class="section-heading">政治信条</h2>
      <div class="belief-box">
        <p class="belief-intro">
          「すべての住民が安心して暮らせる社会」を実現するため、以下の信条のもと活動しています。
        </p>
        <ul class="belief-list">
          <li class="belief-item">住民の声を第一に、現場主義を徹底します</li>
          <li class="belief-item">透明性の高い政治を実現します</li>
          <li class="belief-item">次世代に誇れる地域づくりを推進します</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="profile-cta">
      <a href="/policy/" class="cta-button primary">政策を見る</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="cta-button secondary">お問い合わせ</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</main>

<style>
.modern-profile {
  padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
}

.page-title {
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  color: var(--modern-primary);
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
  position: relative;
  padding-bottom: 1rem;
}

.page-title::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  width: 60px;
  height: 4px;
  background: var(--modern-accent);
  border-radius: 2px;
}

.profile-intro {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--modern-primary) 0%, var(--modern-accent) 100%);
  color: #fff;
  padding: 3rem 2rem;
  border-radius: 16px;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.intro-title {
  font-size: 2rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  margin-top: 0;
}

.intro-subtitle {
  font-size: 1.125rem;
  opacity: 0.95;
}

.profile-section {
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.section-heading {
  font-size: 1.75rem;
  color: var(--modern-primary);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  border-bottom: 2px solid var(--modern-border);
}

.info-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  gap: 1rem;
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .info-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }
}

.info-item {
  background: var(--modern-bg-light);
  padding: 1.5rem;
  border-radius: 8px;
  border-left: 4px solid var(--modern-accent);
}

.info-label {
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  color: var(--modern-text-light);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  font-weight: 600;
}

.info-value {
  font-size: 1.125rem;
  color: var(--modern-text);
}

.timeline {
  position: relative;
  padding-left: 2rem;
}

.timeline::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  top: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  width: 2px;
  background: var(--modern-border);
}

.timeline-item {
  position: relative;
  padding-bottom: 2rem;
}

.timeline-item::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  left: -2.5rem;
  top: 0.25rem;
  width: 12px;
  height: 12px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--modern-accent);
  border: 2px solid #fff;
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--modern-accent);
}

.timeline-year {
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--modern-primary);
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}

.timeline-content {
  color: var(--modern-text);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.belief-box {
  background: var(--modern-bg-light);
  padding: 2rem;
  border-radius: 12px;
}

.belief-intro {
  font-size: 1.125rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  color: var(--modern-text);
}

.belief-list {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
}

.belief-item {
  padding: 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: 8px;
  border-left: 4px solid var(--modern-accent);
  color: var(--modern-text);
}

.profile-cta {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1rem;
  align-items: center;
  margin-top: 3rem;
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .profile-cta {
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-content: center;
  }
}

.cta-button {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
  border-radius: 50px;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  min-width: 200px;
  text-align: center;
}

.cta-button.primary {
  background: var(--modern-primary);
  color: #fff;
}

.cta-button.primary:hover {
  background: var(--modern-primary-dark);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 12px var(--modern-shadow);
}

.cta-button.secondary {
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--modern-primary);
  border: 2px solid var(--modern-primary);
}

.cta-button.secondary:hover {
  background: var(--modern-primary);
  color: #fff;
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}
</style>
